{"id":"b9016d9d-88ec-4792-a1dd-b88c8d981213","name":"Waylen & Reggie","description":"<hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">[Nº11]</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Let's start from the beginning:</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>New city, new life. You just came to this hell hole of a city in search of something. What exactly? You are not so sure...but you feel drawn to the shady, dangerous but extremely profitable opportunities that you have been told it offers, set on making yourself a name in there.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>First stop? You should start making some contacts...or maybe enemies? That's something to decide later. For now, you want to see what this place has to offer, what you can play with so to say.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Lets see how this turns out.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/519285de-ed90-42d8-8cd1-a14890b287cd_3c8ff83a-06a4-4a3c-bdd4-a82af5a506f1.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 847px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">[ART]</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;opi=89978449&amp;url=https://twitter.com/Maggotnizer%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Egoogle%257Ctwcamp%255Eserp%257Ctwgr%255Eauthor&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi5vLHXkfaJAxX1Q6QEHX-JKVUQ6F56BAgQEAE&amp;sqi=2&amp;usg=AOvVaw3QALclypcqAdmyZ4IpAWeW\" target=\"_blank\">Maggotnizer</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"t